Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:06.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There once was a pony who travelled the land
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:10.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With a smile~ as bright as the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:15.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She went town to town as a one pony band
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:19.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sharing smiles with ev'ryone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:24.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She always sang loudly so all could hear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:28.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her words that she sang~ with glee
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:33.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And all the townponies they all~ did cheer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:37.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For this mare as pink as candy, oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:42.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This pink pony bard~, this bright young mare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:44.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Whose smiles~ and songs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:46.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,turned towns upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:51.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh pink pony bard with your songs of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,May there never be a day that you frown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:57.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This small pony sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:59.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,to her own heart's content
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:04.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From the morning to the dark~ of night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:09.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She made ev'ryday feel like one big event
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:13.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And she always was cheerful and bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The townponies claim
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:18.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,that her songs were like spells
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:22.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For that no bard has done that before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:27.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her music just made all their emotions swell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:31.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She was one pony none could ignore, oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:36.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Pink pony bard~, one with such flare
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:38.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Whose grand sing-alongs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:40.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,went through all of town
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:45.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh pink pony bard with your songs of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:48.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,May there never be a day that you frown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When the pink pony left
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,there were tears to be shed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:58.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For there was no one bard~ like she
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her songs were so loved
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,and they all soon were spread
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:07.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Across the land and through the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:12.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her name though unknown by most ponykind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:16.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her songs are still sung to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But if you look and you listen I'm
